**Key Responsibilities:**

- Develop new sales leads and build our customer portfolio.
- Work in a highly autonomous environment.
- Utilize technology resources and business relationships as sales vehicles.
- Approach tasks in a detailed and organized fashion.
- Achieve growth and maximize income potential while building meaningful relations.
- Proactively target key industries to expand the already established client base.
- Meet all KPI's and generate revenue for your region.
- Leverage off any existing relationships and network effectively to develop relationships and ultimately win business.

**Skills/Competencies:**

- Sales and Operational experience in the Forwarding industry.
- Knowledge of all facets of the end-to-end Freight Forwarding services.
- Energetic, self-motivated, and proactive in sourcing new business.
- Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal.
- Detail-oriented and organized.
- Self-directed, self-driven, and entrepreneurial attitude.
- Experience utilizing technology resources and business relationships as sales vehicles.
- Ability to exceed sales targets within a competitive sector.

